public class AIXOperatingSystemImpl
extends OperatingSystemImpl
implements AIXOperatingSystem

An implementation of the model object 'AIX Operating System'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Desktop
  • Install Date
  • Kernel
  • Last Boot Up Time
  • Owner
  • TCB
